snippet.title: Infinite Cake Anyone? _ Slow Version
snippet.description: Still experimenting with cake! Here I show and explain how to cut out a piece of cake from a slab of cake, cut and rearrange what remains and create a complete whole copy of the original cake. If you do this an infinite number of times (see the bonus footage at the end of the video) you will have an infinite supply of cake! Woohoo!
